invalid type: string "Q: What is the semester fee for PHD Mathematics?\nA: The semester fee is Rs. 83,000 per semester for Spring 2026.\n\nQ: Is there an admission fee for PHD Mathematics?\nA: Yes. A one-time admission fee of Rs. 22,000 is charged at the time of admission. It is paid only once and is non-refundable.\n\nQ: What is the total cost in the first semester of PHD Mathematics?\n’’’’’’’’’’